details: Dell Inspiron 15 3511 Laptop comes with Intel Intel Core i3-1115G4 Processor (6M Cache, 3.00 GHz up to 4.10 GHz) with Intel UHD Graphics. From this laptop you will get the best combination of Windows features. This new Dell Inspiron 15 3511 featured with 4GB DDR4 RAM, 1TB 5400 rpm 2.5in SATA Hard Drive with Windows 10 Home Operating System. Here, 2 x USB 3.2, 1 x USB 2.0, 1 x HDMI 1.4, 1 x Audio jack Ports,Connectors & Slots are also available. It is Designed to last through regular use, with tiny rubber feet and bumpers on the hinge that keep it from skidding and provide additional stability on hard surfaces. This Dell Inspiron 15 3511 Laptop featured with 3-Cell Battery, 41WHr (Integrated). Here, the built-in HD webcam that makes you look great. This Dell Inspiron laptop is made from 100% recycled paper, while other packaging components are comprised of up to 90% recycled materials. The Laptop has 802.11ac 1x1 WiFi and Bluetooth. This latest Dell Inspiron 15 3511 Laptop has 02 Years Warranty (Battery and Adapter 2 Years).
